<p>Serious question,</p>
<p>What is the process, life, and workload of staff? Is this a cool kids club? Do you guys get paid?</p>
<p>I would encourage all staff to answer this actually. I know the answers to most of this, but I'm not sure a lot of the users understand the kind of workload on staff.</p>
<p>So, staff, describe WHAT YOU DO on a daily basis for this totally-not-for-money, volunteer thing you do.</p>

